    "EmpathyEmpathy in the context of AI underscores the importance of maintaining the human aspect of health care, especially as AI technologies become more prevalent.",
    "ExplainabilityExplainability in AI in medicine is closely linked to transparency and is important for understanding the AI-based decision-making process, affecting physician-patient relationships, and shared decision-making.",
